  <brief_title>Study Comparing Pulmonary Vein Isolation With the Cryoballoon and Radiofrequency Energy(Contact Force) in the Treatment of Persistent Atrial Fibrillation (AF) (Cryo Vs CF in PerAF)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study Comparing Pulmonary Vein Isolation With the Cryoballoon and Radiofrequency Energy(Contact Force) in the Treatment of Persistent Atrial Fibrillation (PerAF)</official_title>
